 Updated Master To-Do List — Centaur-Jarvis v1.0
🧠 Core Principles (Always Active)
✅ 360° Edge Case Anticipation — Har module design mein network failures, WAF blocks, rate limits, hardware constraints, cross-platform paths, data corruption sab socha gaya hai.
✅ No Silent Failures — Har error log hota hai, console pe scream hota hai, Discord alert bheja jata hai. Kabhi except: pass nahi.
✅ Plug-and-Play Modularity — Har module independent, ek fail to baki chalte rahe. Communication sirf Redis ke through.
✅ Performance First — Multi-threading, async, connection pooling, GPU (via Ollama) use karte hain, but rate limits ka dhyan rakhte hain.
✅ Graceful Shutdown — Ctrl+C daba to current tasks finish kare, state save kare, phir exit. Restart pe recover ho.
✅ Idempotency & Recovery — Har task ek unique ID. Duplicate ignore. Crash ke baad wahi se resume.
✅ Telemetry & Logging — Har state change, task routing, error — sab log file + console. Critical alerts Discord pe.
✅ Human-in-the-Loop — AI sirf 90% drudgity (recon, analysis, payload generation) karega. Exploitation aur validation human karega (Burp ya manual).

